|YKOUsage: |YKBareas|YKO
       |YKBareas <world or region>|YKO
       |YKBareas level <number>|YKO
       |YKBareas search <word>|YKO
       |YKBareas info <number>|YKO

The areas command lists public cataloged places to explore. Areas are grouped
by world and region, such as |WKOGeshtai / Darkwind|YKO, |WKOGeshtai / Hyperborea|YKO,
or |WKODailos / Dailos|YKO.

Use |YKBareas search <word>|YKO to find places by name, tag, note, world, or
region. After any list or search, use |YKBareas info <number>|YKO to see more
detail about that area.

The level range is a rough guide based on cataloged monster levels. Some
places contain unusual monsters, bosses, puzzles, or variable-level creatures,
so explore carefully.
